">que deliran ante el eclipse de sol</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">desorientados,</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">responden al instinto de un sol escondido.</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">Hoy sé que por vagar en la noche</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">la noche no se vuelve hermosa</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">pero me llama el canto de las sirenas</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">que me esperan con lo más temido</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">el silencio.</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">Hoy sé que por vagar en la noche</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;ta