ión será natural.</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">COMO EL RAYO</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">13</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">Tú sigues navegando en el espacio</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">azul y magnífica</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">herida de muerte.</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">Tu venganza no es dulce</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">nos arrastras con tus vientos</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">tus huracanes,</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">tus ríos e