s&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">soberbia juventud sonámbula</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">no me ve, no me oye</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">pasa a mi lado</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">de figura de fantasma</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">dejándome la estela</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">del perfume a esperanza.</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">y se prende, mi amor</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">en ese aroma.</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">Yo sé</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , s