cc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">Tus otrora cristalinas aguas</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">invaden los pueblos</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">con nuestras propias pestilencias.</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">El infierno íntimo quema los</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">frondosos bosques.</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">¡IGNORANCIA!</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">Arden la belleza y el oxígeno</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">arden las esperanzas</span><br /><span style="background-color: #1c1c1c; color: #cccccc; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;freesans&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;">mueren especies inocentes.</span><br /><span style